data.description: Tastefully upgraded and meticulously well kept end unit townhome conveniently located in Carson City. Approximately 1 mile to Downtown Carson, 15 miles to Lake Tahoe, 1 mile to the highway. This home features a full 2-car garage, upgraded flooring, 50 gallon water heater less than 1 year old. Upstairs you have three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, an office and laundry room. Half bath is downstairs. Kitchen has a gas cooktop, all appliances are stainless steel and will stay with the property.
